title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
EB: Exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row should not result in an exception being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Add a table to the report that includes a group row, a highlight rule, and a map rule.
2. Preview the report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
